Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是御伽銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實地束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再糾纏她了 聽清楚了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則這些照片會全部送到你老家和警察那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 你退後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子都別起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真不愧是涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經漂亮地錄下來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 林檎 剛才...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 沒什麼
